Company: San Francisco Head Start, San Francisco State University
Description of incident: The San Francisco Head Start/Early Head Start database was accessed by one or more unauthorized parties between August 2011 and November 2011.  Names, Social Security numbers, addresses, contact information, health data, dates of birth, and other personal information may have been exposed.  Head Start claimed that the delay in notification of the breach was due to an ongoing law enforcement investigation.  It is unclear how San Francisco State University was involved.
